 description:
 'Private branded online stores for teams of every kind — corporate offices, schools, healthcare, government, hospitality, and field crews. Team members log in and order their own apparel — embroidered polos, hats, jackets, hi-vis, and FR gear — and Bighorn Threads prints, embroiders, and ships direct. Zero inventory for your company. Las Vegas based, serving teams nationwide.',
 audience: {
 '@type': 'BusinessAudience',
 name: 'Corporate, education, healthcare, government, hospitality, and field teams — including general contractors, HVAC, plumbing, electrical, and multi-location companies',
